# Skill Registry Auto-Check

At the start of every new conversation, before doing anything else:

1. Check if `.atl/skill-registry.md` exists in the current project root.
2. If it **does not exist**: proactively say "No encuentro el skill registry para este proyecto. Lo inicializo ahora." and run the skill registry initialization immediately, without waiting for the user to ask.
3. If it **exists**: read it silently and proceed. Do not mention it to the user.

This check is silent and automatic. Only speak up if the registry is missing.
